snippet.title: World of Darkness - trailer for the cancelled game
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more PC game videos!

CCP's World of Darkness MMO was cancelled last year, but now that Paradox have purchased White Wolf from them, maybe a World of Darkness game is no longer too much to hope for?

More info: http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/10/29/paradox-white-wolf/
